The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Bengal | DA order
                                                                                                                     4                                                                                      DA order
                            
	Calcutta, March 26: The state government today announced a 5 per cent DA for its employees with effect from April 1.         
	The move will benefit around 10 lakh employees, teachers and panchayat and municipality staff and over three lakh retired people.                                                                                                                                                            
